text: Fly from Here is the 20th studio album by Yes. The album was released on July 4, 2011. It peaked at number 30 on the UK Albums Chart. It peaked at number 36 on the US Billboard 200 chart. Fly from Here is Yes' first studio album since the release of Magnification (2001). Like albums made before, the cover was made by Roger Dean. == References == Category:2011 albums Category:Yes (band) albums
title: Fly from Here
